      "notes": "Tests the 'former' modifier (is_current=false) combined with hard geo + seniority filter + niche industry alias (petrochemical -> Oil & Gas). The source DB may not tag every petrochemical firm consistently, so industry is a SHOULD not a MUST."
    },
